'''Timibrikt n Liṭṭunya''' d iri azegraw [[Liṭṭunya|taliṭṭunit]]. Isem-is agraɣlan d '''{{lang|en|latvian brown}}''' dɣa isem-is [[aliṭṭuni]] d '''{{lang|lv|Latvijas brūnā}}''' neɣ ''buraïa latviskaïa'' s [[tarusit|trusit]].
== Taneṣlit ==
D iri aqdim, ixelqe-d seg usegraw n tijlibin tidiganin tiqdimin n taciṭṭa [[tazegwaɣt n Baltik]]. Teḍḍfed tazrirt n [[angeln (iri azegraw)|angeln]] deg {{timiḍi wisXIX}} uqbel alday n [[asaklas asutwalan|usaklas asutwalan]] deg useggwas [[1885]] dɣa teḍḍfed isem-is amiran deg useggwas [[1922]]. Seg zik, nettat d iri n uyefki deg aẓi, mazal t-genses aqrib 75 % n uctal azegraw aliṭṭuni. Iri yettwebḍa s kuẓ ifurkawen yettweṛebban yal yiwen deg umkan is iwakken ad ssineḍen imeccir asiwan. Afurk BL-1 yettwefren s tixxutert taɛlayant deg [[sovkhoz|isubxuzen]]. Tettaked tikessawin n tafarest n uyefki am imzufɣawen. Tafest n iketmen tesgader. Seg {{formatnum:1147000}} deg useggwas [[1980]], Tagrawt yeṣṣub ar {{formatnum:556000}} deg useggwas 1990<ref name="tiho-hannover.de">{{en}} http://www.tiho-hannover.de/einricht/zucht/eaap/descript/143.htm</ref>. Deg useggwas [[2000]], amḍan n imzufɣawen BL-1 yessiggezen ɣef asaklas yella d {{formatnum:60000}} tifunasin d 300 iramulen.
== Tasnalɣa ==
Telsa taqendurt tazegwaɣt s tisignayin timibriktin ugar-neɣ-ddaw tibuḍḍlamin. Ini n mukus ines d ini n uksum dɣa ur tesɛa ara acciwen. <br/>Tafunast taɛlay ar 130&nbsp;cm deg timezsmeḍt i 520&nbsp;kg dɣa aramul 140&nbsp;cm i 800&nbsp;kg<ref name="tiho-hannover.de"/>.
== Iketturen ==
D iri i mmizweren i uyefki. Tettfaras 5200&nbsp;kg s usuḍeḍ n uyefki yesɛan aṭas n tinegwa uzuren (4,16 %) d tifṛutinin. (3,45 %)

